# This directory is for Grafana dashboard JSON files.
#
# Place exported dashboard JSON files here to provision them automatically.
# Grafana will load them on startup.
#
# Example dashboards to create:
#   - inference_metrics.json    # Latency, throughput, error rate
#   - system_resources.json     # CPU, GPU, memory usage
#   - model_performance.json    # Per-model accuracy, drift
#
# Export from Grafana UI: Dashboard → Share → Export → Save to file
# Or create manually following Grafana documentation.
#
# Do not commit sensitive data in dashboards.
